{"id":"13ab4d97-b579-4a0b-bbbd-e431a2e62e50","title":"1510/01/05","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"a23b05e3-afe3-49d0-9098-e719fbcabbb7","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, January 5th, 1510.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"b61fdcaa-d105-4f2e-8e7d-8f0c5d41e2bc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e9abbf44-3e5d-4bb3-9db0-a106ba75226e","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":27,"value":"3ccfbaaf-9d02-4668-9b08-ef1a333436c6","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7da0f676-4f0d-4a24-bb59-257a97076f71","type":"style/superscript","start":20,"end":21,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"30cbc490-85d1-4ea7-af70-1a902df1f74c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"332ee7dc-e1de-4d6f-b8b6-3c08959755ad","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"caf31c34-9e6b-43e0-96ee-3fde13caae48","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"549452c3-586a-4e33-98b6-d7539cb0c94e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"3c7634e2-9d4b-4d9b-aade-e6ff6bd207c6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"ae1471af-064d-4301-a47e-f2c9958e57b8","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f4d7727c-0bb4-4de5-8a55-6da939897c99","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Dearest Father,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0In my last letter I expressed myself as in favour of buying. You now inform me\u00A0that, in addition to Girolamo Cini\u0027s land, you are negotiating for another farm at Pazolatico. I should buy them both if the title deeds are in order, but see that you keep your eyes open and are not involved in lawsuits to follow. Be exceedingly careful to see that you are secure. They speak encouragingly about the house, but I am not expecting much, as I know I shall only be given a free tenancy for the period of my stay here. It is useless to look at it in any other light. Buonarroto writes to me with reference to his getting married. I will tell you what I think of the matter, and it is this: within the next five or six months I hope to set you all free and to make you a present of all the moneys you have had from me up to this day. After that you can all of you do as you please, and in every way possible I will always help every one of you. But advise Buonarroto not to marry before this summer is over: if I were with you I would tell you my reasons. Since he has waited till now, he will not be older in six months\u0027 time. Buonarroto also informs me that Bernardino di Pier Basso desires to come here and enter my service. If that is his desire, let him come at once, before I engage anyone else, for I want to begin work on something or other. As to his wages, I will give him\u00A0what was mentioned, three ducats a month, that is to say, and his expenses. The fact is that my housekeeping is after a simple sort and I do not wish to change it. Tell him what I have said and bid him make haste. If after a week\u0027s trial he does not like being in my service he can return to Florence, and I will give him the money for his journey. There is nothing else I wish to say.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"fb9edc56-2f04-40ea-8bbe-e89e72f4981b","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":13,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"98025c83-a82c-4558-927d-9da025c43190","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":13,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b962fda8-56d4-443b-b392-82675375a06a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,